ector dcr-1c9t5u6"><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">Salvage crews in <a href=3D"htt=
ps://www.theguardian.com/world/fiji" data-link-name=3D"in body link" data-c=
omponent=3D"auto-linked-tag">Fiji</a> are working to prevent an oil spill a=
fter a cruise ship ran aground off the island on which the 2000 Tom Hanks f=
ilm Cast Away was filmed.</p><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">The Blue Lagoon <a hr=
ef=3D"https://www.theguardian.com/travel/cruises" data-link-name=3D"in body=
 link" data-component=3D"auto-linked-tag">Cruises</a> vessel Fiji Princess =
grounded at a reef near the uninhabited Monuriki Island on Saturday, accord=
ing to Fiji=E2=80=99s maritime rescue agency.</p><div id=3D"sign-in-gate"><=
/div><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">All 30 passengers and 17 of its 31 crew were =
taken off the vessel the same day. There have been no injuries reported.</p=
><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">The company has been contacted for comment.</p><g=
