lot ad-slot ad-slot--inline ad-slot--inline1" data-link-name=3D"ad slot inl=
ine1" data-name=3D"inline1" aria-hidden=3D"true"></div></div><p class=3D"dc=
r-130mj7b">=E2=80=9CInitial checks confirmed that the vessel has suffered s=
erious damage to its rear left side, including the area where the steering =
equipment is located. Part of the vessel underneath has also been damaged,=
=E2=80=9D a spokesperson said.</p><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">=E2=80=9CThe ves=
sel also experienced engine failure and was reported to be taking in water =
following the grounding. Due to rough seas and strong waves, officers were =
unable to safely inspect the vessel underwater at the time.=E2=80=9D</p><p =
class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">An Msaf spokesperson said the main priority on Monday=
 was to reduce the risk of pollution.</p><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">The vesse=
l was carrying about 20,000 litres of diesel fuel. The spokesperson said au=
thorities had taken oil spill equipment to the area =E2=80=9Cas a precautio=
n=E2=80=9D but that the sea conditions were too rough for it to be used.</p=
><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">=E2=80=9CAt the time of inspection, there were no=
 signs that the fuel tanks had been damaged,=E2=80=9D the spokesperson said=
.</p><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">Salvage teams were working to remove the fuel=
 and oil from the vessel, with the assistance of a salvage specialist from =
Australia.</p><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">Once the weather improved, further w=
ork would begin to recover the vessel safely, the spokesperson said.</p><p =
class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">=E2=80=9CMsaf=E2=80=99s main concern at this time is =
the safety of all personnel, the protection of Fiji=E2=80=99s marine enviro=
nment, and ensuring that response efforts continue safely,=E2=80=9D they sa=
id.</p><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">=E2=80=9CMsaf will continue to work closely=
 with the vessel operator and all response teams, and will provide further =
updates as necessary.=E2=80=9D</p><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">Monuriki Island,=
 about 45km west of the city of Nadi, was the filming location for the 2000=
 film Cast Away. It is part of the Mamanuca Island chain, on which the US v=
ersion of reality show Survivor has been filmed since 2016.</p><p class=3D"=
dcr-130mj7b">Blue Lagoon Cruises advertises the Fiji Princess as being smal=
l enough to =E2=80=9Cget so close to shore that we can tie off to a coconut=
 tree, and you can swim to the beach=E2=80=9D.</p><p class=3D"dcr-130mj7b">=
Evacuated passengers and crew were taken back to Port Denarau.</p><p class=
=3D"dcr-130mj7b">The remaining crew were aiding salvage efforts, and were b=
eing berthed on Fiji Princess=E2=80=99s sister ship, Cougar, for safety rea=
sons.</p></div></div><gu-island name=3D"SlotBodyEnd" priority=3D"feature" d=
